---
---

<section class="section founder">
  <div class="container prose">
    <div class="founder-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why I'm building this</p>

      <blockquote class="founder-quote">
        <p>
          Last year, I was screenshotting six health apps into ChatGPT every morning
          to get advice. It worked — better than any single app. But the friction
          was ridiculous.
        </p>
        <p>
          Meld is what I wanted to exist. I'm building it for myself first.
          If it works for you too, I'd love to hear about it.
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="founder-signature">
        <div class="avatar" aria-hidden="true">BH</div>
        <div class="sig-text">
          <strong>Brock Howard</strong>
          <span>Founder, Meld · VP Product at Lark Health</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/journal/why-meld" class="read-more">Read the full story →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--r-card-lg);
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .founder-card .eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .founder-quote {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--purple-300);
    padding-left: var(--sp-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .founder-signature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-400) 0%, var(--purple-600) 100%);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sig-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .sig-text strong {
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .sig-text span {
    font-size: var(--fs-caption);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .read-more {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--purple-600);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
  }
</style>
